      <h2 class="title">
      <a href="/node/3581" title="Spring Data Redis 1.0.1 Released">Spring Data Redis 1.0.1 Released</a>
    </h2>
  
  
      <div class="meta">
              <div class="submitted">
          Submitted by Costin Leau on Wed, 2012-06-27 12:32        </div>
      
              <div class="terms terms-inline"> in <ul class="links inline"><li class="taxonomy_term_4 first last active"><a href="/taxonomy/term/4" rel="tag" title="News and announcements
" class="active">News and Announcements</a></li>
</ul></div>
          </div>
  
  <div class="content">
    <p>Dear Spring Community,</p>
<p>I am pleased to announce the GA release of Spring Data Redis 1.0.1 project!</p>
<p><a href="http://www.springsource.com/download/community?project=Spring%20Data%20Redis&amp;version=1.0.1.RELEASE">Downloads</a> | <a href="http://static.springsource.org/spring-data/data-redis/docs/1.0.1.RELEASE/api/">JavaDocs</a> | <a href="http://static.springsource.org/spring-data/data-redis/docs/1.0.1.RELEASE/reference/html">Reference Documentation</a> | <a href="http://static.springframework.org/spring-data/data-redis/docs/1.0.1.RELEASE/changelog.txt">Changelog</a></p>
<p>Spring Data Redis 1.0.1 is more then a maintenance release introducing several new features such as:</p>
  </div>

